# portapop phase 3 KEYS: cast track 1 to KEYS (2 INST-chip taps), record chords, play back.
# INST chip for track 1 is at x=4..76, y=56..68. Two taps: BASS -> DRUM -> KEYS.
press 10 10 61
release 16 10 61
press 30 10 61
release 36 10 61
# record (track 0 armed by default, now KEYS)
tap 50 R
# two struck triads (A/D/G on the GB map = MIDI 60/64/67 = C E G)
tap 210 A
tap 214 D
tap 218 G
tap 340 A
tap 344 D
tap 348 G
tap 520 R
# play back
tap 540 SPACE
